    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sanctae et individuae Trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/79">Hugo</persName> et <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/72">Lotharius</persName> divina favente clementia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">reges</rs>. Si sactorum Dei ecclesiis ex nostris
                        rebus aliquid offerimus, presentis et aeternae vitae bravium adipisci non
                        titubamus. Quapropter omnium sanctae Dei Ecclesiae fidelium nostrorumque
                        presentium ac futurorum industria noverit, qualiter pro Dei amore
                        animarumque nostrarum remedio et pro anima <rs key="#motherOf">matris</rs>
                        nostrae <persName key="#motherOf" ref="#people/1524">Bertae</persName>
                        quandam <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1451">in honore sanctae Mariae</orgName>
                        constructam, in <placeName ref="#places/2721">Monte Ionio</placeName> sitam,
                        cum omnibus rebus et familiis ad eam in integrum pertinentibus, nec non et
                            <rs key="#Landed_possessions">campum</rs> iuxta eandem ecclesiam regiae
                        potestati hactenus pertinentem, atque <geogName
                            key="#Areas #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            ref="#estates/2351">Barbaritanos</geogName> similiter iuris regni nostri
                        pertinentes cum omnibus eorum pertinentiis; insuper et omnem illam <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terram</rs> quam mater nostra ex Camerino <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Inflow #Purchase #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >adquisivit</rs> in <placeName>Monte Ferentino</placeName>, atque <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">sortem</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            ref="#estates/2355">Lauro</geogName> et <geogName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            ref="#estates/2352">Muclani</geogName>, quae regiae parti hactenus
                        pertinuit; insuper etiam <rs key="#Churches">capellam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Churches"
                            >in honore sancti Marini</orgName> constructam cum suis pertinentiis,
                        atque <rs key="#Landed_possessions">sortem</rs> in <geogName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            ref="#estates/2353">Querceto</geogName>, que laboratur per <persName
                            key="#Freeborn"><name ref="Bonipertus">Bonipertum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Freeborn">liberum hominem</rs>, quam <rs key="#brotherOf"
                            >frater</rs> noster <persName key="#brotherOf" ref="#people/1516"
                            >Boso</persName> eidem contulit congregationi, per huius nostri precepti
                        paginam <rs key="#Monks">monachis ac fratribus</rs> in cenobio <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Agricultural_workers #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Churches #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1450">Sanctae Florae Deo</orgName> famulantibus
                        in usum et sumptum illorum concedimus, donamus atque largimur, et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >de nostro iure et dominio in eorum ius et dominium</rs> omnimodis
                        transfundimus ac delegamus, ut in illorum stipendium predicta predia
                        maneant, ipsique habeant, teneant, firmiterque possideant posterique illorum
                        iure perpetuo. Et si aliquis episcopus aut quislibet Dei inimicus prefatas
                        res cenobitis Sanctae Florae ullo in tempore tulerit, aut quolibet ingenio
                        abstrahere quesierit, tunc deveniant ipsae res in ius et potestatem
                        propinquiorum parentum nostrorum, donec talis potestas venerit, qui
                        fratribus ac cenobitis easdem res reddat et tenere faciat. Insuper etiam
                        omnes res et familias, quae constructor eiusdem loci prefato ceobio
                        contulit, et cuncta ab aliis collata fidelibus per hoc idem preceptum
                        confirmamus et corroboramus. Insuper etiam tam monachos quamque <rs>illorum
                            familiam</rs> et <rs key="#Agricultural_workers">massarios</rs>
                        cunctasque res eiusdem cenobii sub nostrae <rs
                            key="#Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium">defensionis mundburdum</rs> recipimus,
                        precipientes ut nullus dux, marchio, comes, aut quislibet homo predictum
                        cenobium de rebus suis disvestire absque legali iuditio audeat. Si quis
                        igitur huius precepti violator extiterit, sciat se compositurum <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras quinquaginta</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Camera_regis">medietatem kamerae nostrae</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem predicto
                            cenobio</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur, manibus propriis roborantes
                        anulum nostrum subter inprimere iussimus. Signa piissimorum (MF) (MF)
                        Hugonis et Lotharii regum. <persName key="#Chancellor"><name
                                ref="Gisbrandus">Giseprandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> ad vicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/1530">Azonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovi et subscripsi. (SR) (SID). Data pridie
                        kal. iunii, anno dominicae incarnationis DCCCCXXXVIIII, regni domni
                        Hugon[i]s regis XIII, filii eius Lotharii regis VII, indictioneXI. Actum
                            <placeName ref="#places/2752">Perusii</placeName>. Feliciter, amen.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
